&gt; it, the sound of horses’ hooves resounded 
&gt; through the forest. Within seconds, five 
&gt; elves on horseback burst into the clearing. 
&gt; Four were heavily armored and their leader 
&gt; wore elegant clothes. A white cloak billowed 
&gt; from his back. 
&gt; “Who the ‘ell are you?” Pigorsh said with 
&gt; his customary courtesy. 
